if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我叫定班人頭入黎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">抄文後扮道歉 刪聲明召網軍》<br />\n渾水定Fortune Insight無恥啲？</span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span><a href=\"https://lih.kg/2504603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2504603</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">【散戶剎星】幕後發功捧100毛上市 <br />\n「大凌張」供股合股一頸血</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170727/720pix/1501157265_7af1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170727%2F720pix%2F1501157265_7af1.png&h=9ca2c8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛記上市，保薦人是「長雄證券」，有玩股票的資深股民必定對這個名字刻骨銘心。長雄與其「揸FIT人」，有大凌張之稱的張志誠，都有不少威水史。長雄過往負責包銷的股票，例如人人控股，先二十五股合二，再每兩股供十七新股，供股價一仙六，較當時股價折讓九成。而原本股價一毫的數字地球，一供十一，每股一仙五，也較市價低九成。 而由他掌控的總壇大凌集團，也曾五次供股，再來一百合一，殺得散戶一頸血，最多損失九成七。<br />\n<br />\n大凌張是股壇的「風雲人物」外，亦捲入多宗官非。"},{"pid":"0cd4d7c05cddd474a0a208d9103185a6a62a1ada","tid":2507301,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"當大家今日為咗東方昇走去買既時候，會唔會突然發現，<br />\n原來仲有幾手當年俾水哥水咗去買既蟹貨 ？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfN2kLocmYS6BGCp67pXo26V7VTbn3fh1o1tYSy5eSJTf?filename=4mayPkC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mayPkC.png&h=252edd67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcXn354hWrdvGvzq5dYZx4YzhK9qCnkQSPeL7P9WV7KK4?filename=Kuic4UH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuic4UH.png&h=5e11e6ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01f73a97112f4d90e14e02ee846c5a8474a96ed9","tid":2507301,"uid":64953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T